quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  44,17,Dájúdájú A dán àwọn ènìyàn Fir‘aon wò ṣíwájú wọn. Òjíṣẹ́ alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé sì dé wá bá wọn
  44,18,"(Ó sọ pé): “Ẹ kó àwọn ẹrúsìn Allāhu lé mi lọ́wọ́. Dájúdájú èmi ni Òjíṣẹ́ olùfọkàntán fun yín"
  44,19,Ẹ má ṣe ṣègbéraga sí Allāhu. Dájúdájú èmi ti mú ẹ̀rí pọ́nńbélé wá ba yín
  44,20,Dájúdájú Èmi sá di Olúwa mi àti Olúwa yín pé kí ẹ má ṣe sọ mí lókò pa
  44,21,"Tí ẹ kò bá sì gbà mí gbọ́, ẹ fi mí sílẹ̀ jẹ́"
  44,22,"Nítorí náà, ó pe Olúwa rẹ̀ pé dájúdájú àwọn wọ̀nyí ni ìjọ ẹlẹ́sẹ̀"
  44,23,"(Allāhu sọ pé): \"Mú àwọn ẹrúsìn Mi rìn ní alẹ́ (nítorí pé) wọn yóò tọ̀ yín lẹ́yìn"
  44,24,Kí o sì fi agbami odò sílẹ̀ ní yíyanu sílẹ̀ bẹ́ẹ̀. Dájúdájú àwọn ni ọmọ ogun tí A máa tẹ̀rì sínú agbami
  44,25,Mélòó mélòó nínú àwọn ọgbà oko àti odò ìṣẹ́lẹ̀rú tí wọ́n fi sílẹ̀ (lẹ́yìn ìparun wọn)
  44,26,Àti àwọn irúgbìn pẹ̀lú àyè àpọ́nlé (tí wọ́n fi sílẹ̀)
  44,27,Àti ìdẹ̀ra tí wọ́n ń gbádùn nínú rẹ̀ (ṣíwájú ìparun wọn)
  44,28,Báyẹn (ni ọ̀rọ̀ wọn ṣe rí). A sì jogún (ìlú) wọ́n fún ìjọ ènìyàn mìíràn
  44,29,"Nígbà náà, sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ kò sunkún wọn. Wọn kò sì fi ìyà wọn falẹ̀"
  44,30,Dájúdájú A gba àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl là nínú ìyà yẹpẹrẹ
  44,31,(A là wọ́n) lọ́wọ́ Fir‘aon. Dájúdájú ó jẹ́ onígbèéraga. Ó sì wà nínú àwọn alákọyọ
  44,32,A kúkú ṣà wọ́n lẹ́ṣà lórí àwọn ẹ̀dá (àsìkò tiwọn) pẹ̀lú ìmọ̀
  44,33,A sì fún wọn ní àwọn àmì tí àdánwò pọ́nńbélé wà nínú rẹ̀
  44,34,Dájúdájú àwọn wọ̀nyí ń wí pé
  44,35,Kò sí ikú kan àyàfi ikú àkọ́kọ́ (tí ó pa wá nílé ayé). Wọn kò sì níí gbé wa dìde
  44,36,"(Bí bẹ́ẹ̀ kọ́), ẹ mú àwọn bàbá wa wá tí ẹ bá jẹ́ olódodo"
  44,37,Ṣé àwọn ni wọ́n lóore jùlọ ni tàbí àwọn ènìyàn Tubba‘u àti àwọn t’ó ṣíwájú wọn? A pa wọ́n rẹ́; dájúdájú wọ́n jẹ́ ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀
  44,38,"A kò ṣẹ̀dá àwọn sánmọ̀, ilẹ̀ àti ohunkóhun tí ń bẹ láààrin méjèèjì pẹ̀lú eré ṣíṣe"
  44,39,"A kò dá àwọn méjèèjì bí kò ṣe pẹ̀lú òdodo, ṣùgbọ́n ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn ni kò mọ̀"
  44,40,"Dájúdájú ọjọ́ òpínyà (ìyẹn, ọjọ́ àjíǹde) ni àkókò àdéhùn fún gbogbo wọn pátápátá"
  44,41,Ní ọjọ́ tí ọ̀rẹ́ kan kò níí fi kiní kan rọ ọ̀rẹ́ kan lọ́rọ̀. A ò sì níí ràn wọ́n lọ́wọ́
  44,42,"Àyàfi ẹni tí Allāhu bá kẹ́. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun ni Alágbára, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"
  44,43,Dájúdájú igi zaƙūm
  44,44,ni oúnjẹ ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀
  44,45,Ó dà bí epo gbígbá tí ń hó nínú ikùn
  44,46,(t’ó) dà bí híhó omi gbígbóná
  44,47,Ẹ mú un. Kí ẹ wọ́ ọ sáàrin gbùngbùn inú iná Jẹhīm
  44,48,"Lẹ́yìn náà, ẹ rọ́ ìyà olómi gbígbóná lé e lórí"
  44,49,"Tọ́ ọ wò (ṣebí) dájúdájú ìwọ ni alágbára, alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé (gẹ́gẹ́ bí ó ṣe pe ara rẹ)"
  44,50,Dájúdájú (ìyà) èyí ni n̄ǹkan tí ẹ̀ ń ṣeyèméjì nípa rẹ̀
  44,51,Dájúdájú àwọn olùbẹ̀rù Allāhu yóò wà ní àyè ìfàyàbalẹ̀
  44,52,(Wọn yóò wà) nínú àwọn Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra pẹ̀lú àwọn omi ìṣẹ́lẹ̀rú (ní ìsàlẹ̀ rẹ̀)
  44,53,Wọn yóò máa wọ aṣọ àrán fẹ́lẹ́fẹ́lẹ́ àti àrán t’ó nípọn; wọn yó sì máà kọjú síra wọn
  44,54,Báyẹn (ni ọ̀rọ̀ wọn yó ṣe rí). A sì máa fi àwọn obìnrin ẹlẹ́yinjú-ẹgẹ́ ṣe ìyàwó fún wọn
  44,55,Wọn yóò máa bèèrè fún gbogbo n̄ǹkan eléso nínú (Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra) pẹ̀lú ìfàyàbalẹ̀
  44,56,Wọn kò níí tọ́ ikú wò níbẹ̀ àyàfi ikú àkọ́kọ́ (tí wọ́n ti kú nílé ayé). (Allāhu) sì máa ṣọ́ wọn níbi ìyà iná Jẹhīm
  44,57,Ó jẹ́ oore àjùlọ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ. Ìyẹn ni èrèǹjẹ ńlá
  44,58,"Nítorí náà, A ṣe (al-Ƙur’ān) ní ìrọ̀rùn lórí ahọ́n rẹ̀ nítorí kí wọ́n lè lo ìrántí"
  44,59,"Nítorí náà, máa retí . Dájúdájú àwọn náà ń retí"
  45,1,Hā mīm
  45,2,"Tírà náà sọ̀kalẹ̀ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu, Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n"
  45,3,Dájúdájú nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ àwọn àmì wà (nínú wọn) fún àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo
  45,4,Àwọn àmì wà nínú ìṣẹ̀dá yín àti ohun tí Allāhu ń fọ́nká (sórí ilẹ̀) nínú àwọn n̄ǹkan abẹ̀mí; (àmì wà nínú wọn) fún ìjọ t’ó ní àmọ̀dájú
  45,5,"(Nínú) ìtẹ̀léǹtẹ̀lé àti ìyàtọ̀ òru àti ọ̀sán, àti ohun tí Allāhu ń sọ̀kalẹ̀ ní arísìkí, tí Ó ń fi sọ ilẹ̀ di àyè lẹ́yìn t’ó ti kú àti ìyípadà atẹ́gùn, àwọn àmì tún wà (nínú wọn) fún ìjọ t’ó ní làákàyè"
  45,6,"Ìwọ̀nyí ni àwọn āyah Allāhu tí À ń ké (ní kéú) fún ọ pẹ̀lú òdodo. Nítorí náà, ọ̀rọ̀ wo lẹ́yìn (ọ̀rọ̀) Allāhu àti àwọn àmì Rẹ̀ ni wọn yóò tún gbàgbọ́"
  45,7,"Ègbé ni fún aládàápaarọ́, ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀"
  45,8,"t’ó ń gbọ́ àwọn āyah Allāhu, tí wọ́n ń ké e fún un, lẹ́yìn náà, tí ó (tún) takú ní ti ìgbéraga bí ẹni pé kò gbọ́ ọ. Fún un ní ìró ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro"
  45,9,"Nígbà tí ó bá nímọ̀ nípa kiní kan nínú àwọn āyah Wa, ó máa mú un ní n̄ǹkan yẹ̀yẹ́. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni ìyà tí í yẹpẹrẹ ẹ̀dá ń bẹ fún"
  45,10,Iná Jahanamọ wà níwájú wọn. Ohun tí wọ́n ṣe níṣẹ́ àti ohun tí wọ́n mú ní aláàbò lẹ́yìn Allāhu kò sì níí rọ̀ wọ́n lọ́rọ̀ kan níbi ìyà. Ìyà ńlá sì wà fún wọn
  45,11,"Èyí ni ìmọ̀nà. Àwọn t’ó sì ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú àwọn āyah Olúwa wọn, ìyà ẹlẹ́gbin ẹlẹ́ta-eléro wà fún wọn"